"Perform the following steps as user <tt class=\"file-path\">Administrator</tt>.</p>\n" +
"\n" +
"\n" +
"<ol class=\"STEPLIST\"><li class=\"STEPLIST\" id=\"THSSTYLE2\">Create a directory <tt class=\"file-path\">backup</tt> within <tt class=\"file-path\">C:\\ebid\\SSL\\CA</tt></li><li class=\"STEPLIST\" id=\"THSSTYLE2\">Copy the following files to <tt class=\"file-path\">C:\\ebid\\SSL\\CA\\backup</tt> directory.\n" +
"<ul>\n" +
