"<ul>\n" +
"<li class=\"UNORD\" id=\"THSSTYLE1\"><tt class=\"file-path\">C:\\ebid\\SSL\\backup\\orig\\server.xml</tt></li>\n" +
"<li class=\"UNORD\" id=\"THSSTYLE1\"><tt class=\"file-path\">C:\\ebid\\SSL\\backup\\orig\\web.xml</tt></li></ul></li><li class=\"STEPLIST\" id=\"THSSTYLE2\">Copy the following directory to <tt class=\"file-path\">C:\\ebid\\SSL\\CA\\backup</tt>\n" +
"<ul>\n" +
"<li class=\"UNORD\" id=\"THSSTYLE1\"><tt class=\"file-path\">C:\\ebid\\SSL\\CA\\cert</tt><dl class=\"note\"><dt><b>Note: &nbsp;</b></dt><dd>Delete the directory <tt class=\"file-path\">C:\\ebid\\SSL\\CA\\cert</tt>. <p>\n" +
