"</dd></dl><br /></li></ul></li><li class=\"STEPLIST\" id=\"THSSTYLE2\">Restart Tomcat server. Go to <b>Start &gt; Programs\n" +
"&gt; SAP Business Intelligence &gt; SAP BusinessObjects BI platform 4 &gt;\n" +
"Central Configuration Manager</b>. Right click <tt class=\"file-path\">Apache\n" +
"Tomcat for BI 4</tt> and select <tt class=\"LITERALMONO\">Restart</tt>.<p>\n" +
"Wait until <b>Apache Tomcat for BI 4</b> is shown as <b>Running</b>.</p>\n" +
"<dl class=\"note\"><dt><b>Note: &nbsp;</b></dt><dd>Refer section on <em class=\"LOWEMPH\">Unable to restart Tomcat\n" +
"via Central Configuration Manager</em> in <a href='javascript:parent.parent.parent.showAnchor(\"EBID-SAG\")' class=\"xref\">Reference [11]</a> for details on an issue seen during Tomcat restart via Central\n" +
"Configuration Manager.</dd></dl><br /></li><li class=\"STEPLIST\" id=\"THSSTYLE2\">Go to <b>Start &gt; Programs &gt; SAP Business Intelligence\n" +
"&gt; SAP BusinessObjects BI platform 4 &gt; SAP BusinessObjects BI platform\n" +
"Java BI Launch Pad</b>.<p>\n" +
"This will open a browser session and launch <b>BI Launch Pad</b>.</p>\n" +
"<dl class=\"note\"><dt><b>Note: &nbsp;</b></dt><dd>The URL in the address bar shows <a href=\"http://&lt;BIS-hostname&gt;:8080/BOE/BI\" title=\"http://&lt;BIS-hostname&gt;:8080/BOE/BI\" target=\"ALEX_EXTERNAL\">http://&lt;BIS-hostname&gt;:8080/BOE/BI</a></dd></dl><br /></li></ol>\n" +
"\n"+
"</div>\n";

var C4_2_6_3=
"<div id=\"content\" class=\"body-content\">\n"+
"<h4><span class=\"CHAPNUMBER\">4.2.6.3 &nbsp; </span><span class=\"CHAPTITLE\"><a name=\"id_o0j4\"></a><a name=\"CHAPTER4.2.6.3\" href='javascript:parent.parent.sC2(\"TOP\")' class=\"CHAPLINK\">CA Signed Certificate Renewal</a></span></h4>\n" +
"\n" +
"<p>\n" +
"This session describes the procedure to renew the CA signed certificate.</p>\n" +
"\n" +
"\n" +
"<ol class=\"STEPLIST\"><li class=\"STEPLIST\" id=\"THSSTYLE2\">Disable the HTTPS configuration on the BIS, refer to section <a href='javascript:parent.parent.parent.showAnchor(\"CAdisable\")' class=\"xref\">Section  4.2.6.2</a>.</li><li class=\"STEPLIST\" id=\"THSSTYLE2\">Create a new CSR file by executing the steps 1 to 5 in\n" +
"section <a href='javascript:parent.parent.parent.showAnchor(\"enable\")' class=\"xref\">Section  4.2.6.1</a>.</li><li class=\"STEPLIST\" id=\"THSSTYLE2\">Login to the OMSAS as <tt class=\"file-path\">root</tt> or <tt class=\"file-path\">CAAS user</tt>.</li><li class=\"STEPLIST\" id=\"THSSTYLE2\">Execute the following command with a proper reason code.<p>\n" +
"<tt class=\"input\"><b>/opt/ericsson/cadm/bin/pkiAdmin cred eniq renew &ndash;csr\n" +
"/var/tmp/ebid/tomcatssl.csr -reason &lt;<i class=\"var\">reasoncode</i>></b></tt></p>\n" +
"<p>\n" +
"Following Parameter should be modified:</p>\n" +
"<p>\n" +
"<tt class=\"file-path\">&lt;<i class=\"var\">reasoncode</i>></tt>- Proper reason\n" +
"code. For further information on the reason codes, refer to chapter\n" +
"describing <strong class=\"MEDEMPH\">Command Appendix</strong> and <strong class=\"MEDEMPH\">Reason Codes</strong> in <a href='javascript:parent.parent.parent.showAnchor(\"rft-OMSec-SAG-ref\")' class=\"xref\">Reference [4]</a></p>\n" +
"</li><li class=\"STEPLIST\" id=\"THSSTYLE2\">Verify request file contents when printed out.</li><li class=\"STEPLIST\" id=\"THSSTYLE2\">Type <b>Y</b> to renew certificate.</li><li class=\"STEPLIST\" id=\"THSSTYLE2\">Verify renewal status of the certificate with the following\n" +
"command. There must be two credentials the new one with &quot;valid&quot; status and the old one with &quot;under renewal&quot; status.<p>\n" +
"<tt class=\"input\"><b>/opt/ericsson/cadm/bin/pkiAdmin cred eniq list</b></tt></p>\n" +
"</li><li class=\"STEPLIST\" id=\"THSSTYLE2\">Revoke the old certificate with the proper common name\n" +
":<p>\n" +
"<tt class=\"input\"><b>/opt/ericsson/cadm/bin/pkiAdmin cred eniq revoke_old &ndash;cn\n" +
"&lt;<i class=\"var\">common name</i>></b></tt></p>\n" +
"<p>\n" +
"Following parameter should be modified:</p>\n" +
"<p>\n" +
"<tt class=\"file-path\">&lt;<i class=\"var\">common name</i>></tt> - BIS host\n" +
"name in capital letters.</p>\n" +
"</li><li class=\"STEPLIST\" id=\"THSSTYLE2\">Check renewal status by listing credentials. The new credential\n" +
"with the given common name must have &lsquo;valid&rsquo; status and\n" +
"the old one is revoked, therefore missing:<br /><tt class=\"input\"><b>/opt/ericsson/cadm/bin/pkiAdmin\n" +
"cred eniq list</b></tt></li><li class=\"STEPLIST\" id=\"THSSTYLE2\">The renewed certificate will be created under <tt class=\"file-path\">/opt/ericsson/csa/certs</tt> directory, move this certificate\n" +
"to <tt class=\"file-path\">/var/tmp/ebid</tt> directory.<p>\n" +
"<tt class=\"input\"><b>mv /opt/ericsson/csa/cert/cert.pem /var/tmp/ebid</b></tt></p>\n" +
"</li><li class=\"STEPLIST\" id=\"THSSTYLE2\">Execute instructions starting from the step on <strong class=\"MEDEMPH\">Exporting\n" +
"Private Key </strong> till the end of section <a href='javascript:parent.parent.parent.showAnchor(\"enable\")' class=\"xref\">Section  4.2.6.1</a></li></ol>\n" +
"\n" +
"\n" +
"\n"+
"</div>\n";

var C4_3=
"<div id=\"content\" class=\"body-content\">\n"+
"<h2><a name=\"ENIQEventsHTTPS\"></a><span class=\"CHAPNUMBER\">4.3 &nbsp; </span><span class=\"CHAPTITLE\"><a name=\"id_156i\"></a><a name=\"CHAPTER4.3\" href='javascript:parent.parent.sC2(\"TOP\")' class=\"CHAPLINK\">HTTPS\n" +
"and ENIQ Events UI</a></span></h2>\n" +
"\n" +
"<p>\n" +
"From ENIQ Events 13B, the Events UI supports the use of HTTPS.\n" +
"HTTPS is configured and enabled by default during initial installation\n" +
"and upgrades to 13B onwards. </p>\n" +
"\n" +
"<p>\n" +
"Upgrades <em class=\"LOWEMPH\">from</em> 13B onwards will reflect\n" +
"the current configuration. Existing certificates will be copied over\n" +
"and HTTPS will be enabled if it was enabled before the upgrade.</p>\n" +
"\n" +
"<dl class=\"note\"><dt><b>Note: &nbsp;</b></dt><dd>HTTPS is not supported by the ENIQ Events UI prior to version\n" +
"13B.</dd></dl><br />\n" +
"<div class=\"ADMON\"><span class=\"ADMONMSG2\">Caution!</span><p class=\"ADMONDESC\">\n" +
"By default, ENIQ Events uses self-signed certificates signed and\n" +
"the SHA1 signature algorithm. If a more secure signature algorithm\n" +
"is required, the customer must either generate their own certificates\n" +
"using OMSAS, or purchase a third party certificate. For more information\n" +
"see <a href='javascript:parent.parent.parent.showAnchor(\"SSL-CA-signed-cert\")' class=\"xref\">Section  4.2.6</a> and <a href='javascript:parent.parent.parent.showAnchor(\"OMSAS\")' class=\"xref\">Section  4.4</a>.</p>\n" +
"</div>\n" +
"\n"+
"</div>\n";

var C4_3_1=
"<div id=\"content\" class=\"body-content\">\n"+
"<h3><span class=\"CHAPNUMBER\">4.3.1 &nbsp; </span><span class=\"CHAPTITLE\"><a name=\"id_sjap\"></a><a name=\"CHAPTER4.3.1\" href='javascript:parent.parent.sC2(\"TOP\")' class=\"CHAPLINK\">Configuration of GlassFish Application\n" +
"Server During Installation and Upgrades</a></span></h3>\n" +
"\n" +
"<p>\n" +
"The ENIQ Events UI runs on the GlassFish Application Server. The\n" +
"following section describes how SSL/HTTPS are configured for GlassFish\n" +
"during initial installation and upgrades to 13B onwards.</p>\n" +
"\n" +
"\n" +
"<ol class=\"STEPLIST\"><li class=\"STEPLIST\" id=\"THSSTYLE2\">Enable Secure Admin Mode<p>\n" +
"To access the GlassFish Admin Console remotely, GlassFish 3.1.2\n" +
"requires that <tt class=\"file-path\">enable-secure-admin</tt> is set.\n" +
"In turn, this requires that GlassFish has a non-empty admin password.\n" +
"The password is empty by default, so the install sets the password\n" +
"and secure admin can then be enabled.</p>\n" +
"</li><li class=\"STEPLIST\" id=\"THSSTYLE2\">Creation of Self-Signed certificates<p>\n" +
"During installation, GlassFish creates a default key store and\n" +
"trust store in the domain's configuration directory <tt class=\"file-path\">&lt;<i class=\"var\">domain-dir</i>&gt;/config</tt>. A self-signed CA certificate\n" +
"is created as a root certificate. A self-signed certificate is created\n" +
"for GlassFish and is signed by the root, and is imported into the\n" +
"key store using the alias <strong class=\"MEDEMPH\">eniq</strong>. It is also\n" +
"imported into the trust store.</p>\n" +
"</li><li class=\"STEPLIST\" id=\"THSSTYLE2\">Configure HTTPS on GlassFish <p>\n" +
"GlassFish receives page requests on Network Listeners and has pre-defined\n" +
"listeners for HTTP and HTTPS on ports 18080 and 8181 respectively. </p>\n" +
"<p>\n" +
"The HTTPS listener is updated to use the previously created self-signed <strong class=\"MEDEMPH\">eniq</strong> cert and security is enabled. \"Port unification\"\n" +
"is used to redirect HTTP request to HTTPS (and vice-versa) and protocols\n" +
"are set up for this.</p>\n" +
"</li><li class=\"STEPLIST\" id=\"THSSTYLE2\">Enable HTTPS<p>\n" +
"Finally, HTTPS is enabled and HTTP requests are set to redirect\n" +
"to HTTPS. </p>\n" +
"<p>\n" +
"The Events UI uses a number of URLs that are hard-coded in the\n" +
"GlassFish <tt class=\"file-path\">domain.xml</tt> file. The URLs are\n" +
"originally defined as HTTP addresses and so they are updated to use\n" +
"HTTPS (and the correct ports).</p>\n" +
"</li><li class=\"STEPLIST\" id=\"THSSTYLE2\">SSL Configuration for GlassFish<p>\n" +
"By default, after installation a GlassFish package has SSL3.0 secured\n" +
"protocol enabled.</p>\n" +
"<p>\n" +
"Perform the following steps to disable <b>SSL3.0</b> for <b>GlassFish</b>.</p>\n" +
"\n" +
"<ol type=\"a\">\n" +
"\n" +
"<li class=\"substep\">Login to the GlassFish Admin Console as user <tt class=\"file-path\">admin</tt>.\n" +
"</li>\n" +
"\n" +
"<li class=\"substep\">Go to <b>Configurations</b> &gt; <b>server-config</b> &gt; <b>Network Config</b> &gt; <b>Protocols</b>,\n" +
"click on the <b>http-listener-2</b>. Then click on the <b>SSL</b> tab on the right panel.\n" +
"</li>\n" +
"\n" +
"<li class=\"substep\">Uncheck the <b>SSL3</b> checkbox and click the <b>SAVE</b> button on the right top to save the settings.\n" +
"</li>\n" +
"</ol></li></ol>\n" +
"<div style=\"margin-top: 12pt\"><a name=\"FIGURE1\">[Missing image SSL3.jpg]</a><p align=\"left\"><i>Figure 1 &nbsp; GlassFish Admin Console</i></p></div>\n" +
"\n"+
"</div>\n";

var C4_3_2=
"<div id=\"content\" class=\"body-content\">\n"+
"<h3><span class=\"CHAPNUMBER\">4.3.2 &nbsp; </span><span class=\"CHAPTITLE\"><a name=\"id_ly62\"></a><a name=\"CHAPTER4.3.2\" href='javascript:parent.parent.sC2(\"TOP\")' class=\"CHAPLINK\">Configuring the BIS for HTTPS</a></span></h3>\n" +
"\n" +
"<p>\n" +
"If Eniq Events has HTTPS enabled or is being used with a BIS that\n" +
"has HTTPS enabled, a new SSL certificate/keystore is required for\n" +
"the BIS.</p>\n" +
"\n" +
"\n" +
"<ol class=\"STEPLIST\"><li class=\"STEPLIST\" id=\"THSSTYLE2\">Ensure that the BIS has HTTPS enabled. For instructions\n" +
