"the <tt class=\"file-path\">KEYSTORE_PASSWD</tt> must be set to <tt class=\"file-path\">tomcatssl</tt>. If <tt class=\"file-path\">KEYSTORE_PASSWD</tt> is not set to <tt class=\"file-path\">tomcatssl</tt>, the ENIQ Events\n" +
"server is not able to communicate with the BIS Server over HTTPS.</dd></dl><br /></li><li class=\"STEPLIST\" id=\"THSSTYLE2\">Login to the presentation server as <tt class=\"file-path\">dcuser</tt> and run the following commands:<p>\n" +
"<tt class=\"input\"><b># cd /eniq/glassfish/glassfish3/glassfish/bin/</b></tt></p>\n" +
"<p>\n" +
"<tt class=\"input\"><b># ./create_bis_keystore.sh &lt;<i class=\"var\">name of BIS</i>></b></tt></p>\n" +
"<p>\n" +
"Where <tt class=\"file-path\">&lt;<i class=\"var\">name of BIS</i>></tt>, is\n" +
"the name of the BIS server. </p>\n" +
"<dl class=\"note\"><dt><b>Note: &nbsp;</b></dt><dd>Use the short name, not the fully qualified domain name.</dd></dl><br /><p>\n" +
"This command produces the path to the new keystore, for example, <tt class=\"file-path\">/eniq/home/dcuser/bis_ssl/tomcatssl.bin</tt>. </p>\n" +
"<p>\n" +
"Copy this file to the BIS.</p>\n" +
"</li><li class=\"STEPLIST\" id=\"THSSTYLE2\">On the BIS, create a backup of the original keystore.\n" +
"For example, open the command prompt and run the following command:<p>\n" +
"<tt class=\"input\"><b># copy C:\\ebid\\SSL\\cert\\tomcatssl.bin C:\\ebid\\SSL\\tomcatssl.bin.bkp</b></tt></p>\n" +
"</li><li class=\"STEPLIST\" id=\"THSSTYLE2\">On the BIS, replace the original keystore with the new\n" +
"keystore created in step 2. For example, if the new keystore has been\n" +
"placed in <tt class=\"file-path\">C:\\temp\\tomcatssl.bin</tt>, open a\n" +
"command prompt and run the following command:<p>\n" +
"<tt class=\"input\"><b># move /Y C:\\temp\\tomcatssl.bin C:\\ebid\\SSL\\cert\\</b></tt></p>\n" +
"</li><li class=\"STEPLIST\" id=\"THSSTYLE2\">On the BIS, restart the Tomcat server, <b>Start &gt;\n" +
"Programs &gt; SAP Business Intelligence &gt; SAP BusinessObjects BI platform\n" +
"4 &gt; Central Configuration Manager</b>. Right click <tt class=\"file-path\">Apache Tomcat for BI 4</tt> and select <tt class=\"LITERALMONO\">Restart</tt>.<p>\n" +
"Wait until <b>Apache Tomcat for BI 4</b> is shown as <b>Running</b>.</p>\n" +
"<dl class=\"note\"><dt><b>Note: &nbsp;</b></dt><dd>Refer section on <em class=\"LOWEMPH\">Unable to restart Tomcat\n" +
"via Central Configuration Manager</em> in <a href='javascript:parent.parent.parent.showAnchor(\"EBID-SAG\")' class=\"xref\">Reference [11]</a> for details on an issue seen during Tomcat restart via Central\n" +
"Configuration Manager.</dd></dl><br /></li><li class=\"STEPLIST\" id=\"THSSTYLE2\"> Login to the presentation server as <tt class=\"file-path\">dcuser</tt> and restart GlassFish. For information on restarting GlassFish refer\n" +
"to <a href='javascript:parent.parent.parent.showAnchor(\"chl2-restartingGlassfish\")' class=\"xref\">Section  3.3</a>.</li><li class=\"STEPLIST\" id=\"THSSTYLE2\">To complete the configuration, login to the mediation\n" +
"server as <tt class=\"file-path\">dcuser</tt> and restart the EC service<p>\n" +
"<tt class=\"input\"><b># ec restart</b></tt></p>\n" +
"</li></ol>\n" +
"<dl class=\"note\"><dt><b>Note: &nbsp;</b></dt><dd>During installation/upgrade, a public version of the root\n" +
"CA certificate is created as <tt class=\"file-path\">/eniq/home/dcuser/bis_ssl/eniqroot_xxxxx.cer</tt>, where <tt class=\"file-path\">xxxxx</tt> is the name of the presentation\n" +
"server. The root CA certificate needs to be installed in users' browsers\n" +
"to access BIS reports. Refer to <a href='javascript:parent.parent.parent.showAnchor(\"InstallCACert\")' class=\"xref\">Section  4.3.3</a> for\n" +
"how to do this.</dd></dl><br />\n" +
"\n"+
"</div>\n";

